{"tid":439781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實唔好成日吹奏港大啦.","createTime":"2017-10-18T06:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T07:12:41.000Z","uid":142222,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d19eb2ca8a945e147cd4a56311a50b3f7cec00a3","tid":439781,"uid":142222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T06:41:31.000Z","msg":"讀得書入到去又點姐<br />\n個品衰個格衰出到黎做野咪又係犯眾憎<br />\n其實CU同KONGU分別好大<br />\n識好多CU畢業 無論係師兄定老師定朋友<br />\n都係好Humble 唔會炫耀自己讀中大<br />\n但讀Kong U果啲都當正自己高人一等 串柒柒<br />\n周圍同人講自己港大畢業<br />\n讀到書但無品唔識做人又有咩用<br />\n睇下偉倫堂班契弟<br />\n咁撚樣造假 扭曲事實 賤到仆街<br />\n已經令到人地對KONG U印象急墮<br />\n可能我圈子有限，會覺得我以偏概全，但起碼我識既人都已經開始唔中意港大。<br />\n<br />\n利申:  UST毒撚一名"},{"pid":"184de5d2eec49a8fe096c6a6208921823daf2705","tid":439781,"uid":142222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T06:42:53.000Z","msg":"有無偉倫撚入黎駁咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff2b3f6ef4464785556372e50ff2a5eafe3973a","tid":439781,"uid":142222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"push push"},{"pid":"39a13111d8128283a8b7aeeeb89e7a857dd666e6","tid":439781,"uid":142222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T06:43:20.000Z","msg":"pishpish"},{"pid":"867cc21d0e1e00f1bef8971e197d46399090cd56","tid":439781,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"偉倫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12f5469bb604a80679ae928c1822d97aafb8548","tid":439781,"uid":142222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T06:49:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd5333f41276ec0f9854edc4e5d0275d3ab8369a","tid":439781,"uid":36580,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:12:41.000Z","msg":"叻啦"}]}